title.narrative: Health Service Delivery & System Support Project

description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) of the Health Service Delivery and System Support Project is to (a) increase the utilization and improve the quality of essential maternal and child health services; and (b) in the event of an Eligible Crisis or Emergency, to provide immediate and effective response to said Eligible Crisis or Emergency.
